          {
            "title": "Relocating Solo to Bengaluru",
            "when": "age 26",
            "event": "He moved alone to Bengaluru for his first full-time analyst role, navigating apartment hunting, setting up a single-person household, and managing all expenses without family support on a starting salary.",
