              },
              {
                "age_when": 24,
                "event": "After marrying and briefly living with her in-laws in a crowded three-bedroom flat in Laxmi Nagar, Priya advocated strongly \u2014 and somewhat anxiously \u2014 for their own separate rental home, navigating that conversation with careful diplomacy to avoid hurting anyone's feelings.",
