              {
                "id": "dca2c322-1cb1-411b-bbfb-59bb78013bce",
                "timestamp": "2026-04-04T06:53:33.815257Z",
                "type": "observation",
                "content": "A defining moment in my life: After marrying and briefly living with her in-laws in a crowded three-bedroom flat in Laxmi Nagar, Priya advocated strongly \u2014 and somewhat anxiously \u2014 for their own separate rental home, navigating that conversation with careful diplomacy to avoid hurting anyone's feelings. \u2014 The experience cemented her identity as someone who prioritizes her nuclear household's harmony above all else while also sharpening her skill of keeping relationships intact through empathetic negotiation.",
                "importance": 8,
                "emotional_valence": 0.0,
                "source_stimulus_id": null,
                "last_accessed": "2026-04-04T06:53:33.815257Z"
