                "timestamp": "2026-04-04T06:53:33.815280Z",
                "type": "observation",
                "content": "A defining moment in my life: Priya joined a neighborhood women's savings circle in her Dwarka apartment complex, contributing \u20b92,000 monthly, and the group quickly evolved into her primary social support network for advice on everything from school admissions to grocery deals. \u2014 Her social confidence grew significantly through this community, reinforcing how much she relies on trusted personal relationships \u2014 rather than institutions or experts \u2014 for guidance on major household decisions.",
